name: Exuberance No. 3 Orange and Teal
description:
Extraordinary energy from Exuberance No. 3 in orange and teal.  Inspiration for this design comes from a supernova.
Exuberance No. 3 Orange and Teal is a one-of-a-kind artistic collaboration that intertwines Tery Spataro's flower photographs and the artificial intelligence of Playform.io to give life to this transfixing new creation. The Exuberance art series are physical surface designs.
